  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Peel and finely dice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Top, tail, peel and finely dice the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong></span></p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786-step-1.new-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786-step-1.new-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786-step-1.new-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786-step-1.new-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786-step-1.new-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong>, <strong>carrot </strong>and <strong>garlic</strong> and cook for 6-8 min or until beginning to caramelise</p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>spaghetti</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p>\n<p>Once cooked, drain and reserve a cup of the <strong>starchy cooking water </strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>vegetables</strong> have softened, add the <strong>beef mince</strong> and cook for 4-5 min further or until browned, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>beef mince</strong> has browned, add the<strong> Henderson's Relish, </strong>1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span><strong> beef stock cube </strong>and<strong> soy sauce</strong> and cook for 1-2 min</p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> and cook for 12-15 min or until the liquid is reduced by half and the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>bolognese sauce </strong></p>\n<p>Meanwhile, grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1786.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
